title: add/modify/remove a meetup
text: to add, modify or remove a meetup, you can contribute a pull request to make the change yourself, file a request to add a new meetup, or open an issue to request the modification or removal of a meetup.

this is a collection of some active tech meetups in the ottawa / gatineau ‚Äúnational capital region‚Äù (ncr).
